'''加文·聖皮雅'''（{{lang-en|Gavin St Pier}}；{{bd|1967年|1月}}），是一名[[根西|根西]]政治人物，在第三次無記名投票後於2016年5月當選為{{le|根西島政策和資源委員會|Policy and Resources Committee of Guernsey|根西島政策和資源委員會主席}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bailiwickexpress.com/jsy/news/gavin-st-pier-guernseys-new-chief-minister-only-just/#.V_SsIyh7pUQ |title=Gavin St Pier is Guernsey's new Chief Minister - but only just... |publisher=Bailiwick Express |date=4 May 2016 |accessdate=2016-12-18 |archive-date=2017-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116083826/http://www.bailiwickexpress.com/jsy/news/gavin-st-pier-guernseys-new-chief-minister-only-just/#.V_SsIyh7pUQ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web  |url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-guernsey-36168498  |title= Gavin St Pier elected as Guernsey States' President  |publisher= BBC  |date= 4 May 2016  |accessdate= 2016-12-18  |archive-date= 2016-09-16  |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160916195822/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-guernsey-36168498  |dead-url= no  }}</ref>。

==簡介==
{{le|2012年根西大選|Guernsey general election, 2012|2012年4月18日的大選}}中，聖皮雅當選為[[根西议会|根西议会]]聖桑普森區的議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-guernsey-17681446 |title=Guernsey election results 2012 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2016-12-18 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701222738/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-guernsey-17681446 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，後來出任根西財政和資源部部長。

